{"word":"χρηματισμός","slug":"χρηματισμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χρηματισμός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χρηματίζω'><el>χρηματίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>an oracular response, divine warning</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>) <i>money making</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <i>gain, profit</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}